          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "排凤与元帅叩头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了，站在一旁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨排凤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢元帅！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "排凤，你不在天波府侍奉太君，你到此做甚？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨排凤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "元帅容禀：太君在将台之上，问道谁人前去敌挡那韩昌，两旁战将无人答应，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨排凤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就命我同孟二爷不分昼夜前来。一路之上，挨挨蹭蹭，把我们的小鞋子都磨破"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨排凤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这是什么话呀？他怎能将你的鞋子都磨破了吓？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨排凤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "元帅你哪里知道：是我同孟二爷一路之上并马而行，鞍碰鞍，蹬碰蹬，天天如"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨排凤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此，我们的鞋怎能磨不破？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这有何妨，改日赔你就是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨排凤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢元帅！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "排凤，我看你年轻幼小，女流之辈，怎能是那韩昌的对手？两军阵前交锋，你"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "凭着何来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨排凤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "元帅听了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨排凤",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "排凤开言道，元帅听根苗：我虽是女子，武艺比人高。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨排凤",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "上阵去，不用枪不用刀，全凭焰火棍一条。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨排凤",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "上打泰山倒，下打北海潮。左打出山虎，右打入洞蛟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨排凤",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "胯下一骑锦战马，嘟噜嘟噜嘟噜爬，掣电追风神鬼号。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨排凤",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "旗开得胜立功劳，同保宋室锦皇朝。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（焦赞上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "单鞭匹马战沙场，扶保杨家把名扬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "元帅在上，焦赞打参！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟少礼，请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀，二哥回来了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "回来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请坐。二哥此番回得朝中，但不知搬来兵有多少，将有几员？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "愚兄此番回朝搬兵，这兵也无有多少，将也无有几员，就是搬来了排凤一人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "排凤在哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "排凤来见过你家焦二爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨排凤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见焦二爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我道排凤定是天神下界，谁知乃是一个黄毛儿的丫头。慢说是交锋打仗，只用"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我一把，也就将她给捏死了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有道是人不可以貌相，水不可以斗量。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "元帅说哪里话！想我弟兄二人，尚且不是大耳韩昌的对手，何况这黄毛的丫头？"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "若要去至阵前，岂不被人耻笑？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟，依你说来，想是看不起排凤么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不错，我就是看她不起！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你既看她不起，你可敢同她较量较量么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要我与他比试呀？好，我倒要领教领教！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你要领教却好，但是你要胜不过她，你便怎样？"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我若胜不过她，我就与她磕头，叫他一声干娘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丈夫一言，可不能反悔。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不反悔。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待本帅与你们作保。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，元帅作保甚好。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此地窄小，到后营比试。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞、杨排凤",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（焦赞、杨排凤同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟，你我同去观看一回。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨延昭、孟良同下。）"
        }
      ],
