      ]
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "孟良",
        "杨延昭",
        "杨排凤",
        "焦赞"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、杨延昭同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "杨延景奉王命统貔貅，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（焦赞、杨排凤双上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "排凤！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨排凤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二爷！"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日你我比试，还是比枪，还是比刀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨排凤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也不用比枪，也不用比刀，你我比棍，你看好不好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "比棍？倒也使得。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨排凤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我取来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（焦赞拾棍。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这棍倒也趁手。来来来，你要小心了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨排凤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二爷请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吹海笛牌子下山歌。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "开言叫排凤，你且听分明，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨排凤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "排凤把话明，二爷休逞能，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨排凤、焦赞同起打，杨排凤打焦赞下。孟良上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "排凤，焦二爷往哪里去了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨排凤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "被我一棍将他打退了，待我赶上前去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你赶上前去，只管着实的打来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨排凤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恐怕焦二爷怪罪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不要紧，有我替你担待。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨排凤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢孟二爷！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孟良下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨排凤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看焦赞甚是凶勇，待我摆阵擒他。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四青衣鬼各持棍同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨排凤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尔等四面拦挡。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四青衣鬼同允。焦赞上。杨排凤、焦赞同起打，焦赞抛棍卧地，四青衣鬼同下。孟良上，扶焦赞。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨排凤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二爷，咱们再战几合！"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "慢来，慢来。我与排凤比试，这上三路、中三路、下三路、棍如旋风一般，只"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（焦赞蹲。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟，你可是服了她么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我服了，排凤真真是个好的！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你可曾记得打赌之事么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打赌之事？什么打赌之事呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你曾在帐中言道，若胜不过排凤，情愿与她磕头，叫声干娘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪里有这等事！我服了她也就完了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他竟要耍赖起来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待本帅问来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "排凤的棍法高强，俺只有招架之功，并无还手之力，排凤是个好的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既是好的，你就该上前陪礼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要俺陪礼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "着呀，向前去叩头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫干娘呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我实在不能叫。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启元帅：焦赞违令。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他既不肯叫——"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "慢来，慢来。只是我叫不出口。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "愚兄在天波府中，早就偏过了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只是我叫不出口，如何是好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我交给你一个方儿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你交给我什么方儿？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就比作那老母鸡下蛋，把脸儿一红，就叫出来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "排凤，我的干娘呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨排凤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喂！"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "真真的晦气呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "后帐排宴，与排凤接风。息兵三日，大战韩昌。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（完）"
        }
